- git mv weave/shared/agents/{types,schema,semconv,constants}.py -> weave/trace_server/agents/ (joins existing chat_view/clickhouse/kafka_events/playground/helpers). op_names.py + __init__.py STAY in weave/shared/agents (op_names is genuinely shared: flow.monitor client + trace_server kafka_events server both import it).
