## Errors & Mistakes
- FIRST sed loop used `for f in $FILES` -- zsh does NOT word-split unquoted vars, so sed got the whole newline-blob as one filename ('File name too long') and changed nothing. Caught by re-grep (all refs still present). Redone with `grep -rl ... | while IFS= read -r f; do sed -i '' ... "$f"; done`.
- Initial smoke test used issubclass() on a non-runtime_checkable Protocol -> TypeError. Re-verified via `AgentsTraceServerInterface in Cls.__mro__` instead.
- The 5 genai mock-spec failures (see above) -- spec'd against the old interface that no longer had genai_otel_export.

